Additionally, the paper focuses on the amplify-and-forward (AF) strategy, which is a common technique in wireless communication and falls under the Communications (cs.COMM) sub-category. Finally, the paper deals with multiple antennas, which is a topic studied in the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
